A Water manometer is attached to a small pressurized air tank with the geometry depicted below. The heights of the depicted points of the system are: [`h_{1} = [$h1]`] [`m`], [`h_{2} = [$h2]`] [`m`], and [`h_{3} = [$h3]`] [`m`]. 

